  "response": "To maintain a healthy liver, consider incorporating these supplements and foods:\n\nFoods:\n1. Leafy green vegetables\n2. Garlic\n3. Turmeric\n4. Grapefruit\n5. Walnuts\n6. Fatty fish (salmon, sardines)\n7. Green tea\n8. Beets\n9. Cruciferous vegetables (broccoli, cauliflower)\n10. Olive oil\n\nSupplements:\n1. Milk thistle\n2. Vitamin D\n3. Omega-3 fatty acids\n4. Probiotics\n5. Vitamin E\n6. N-acetyl cysteine (NAC)\n7. Zinc\n8. B-complex vitamins\n\nAdditional recommendations:\n- Stay hydrated\n- Limit alcohol consumption\n- Maintain a healthy weight\n- Exercise regularly\n- Avoid processed foods\n- Reduce sugar intake\n\nAlways consult with a healthcare professional before starting any new supplement regimen, as individual needs can vary.",
